SIMPLE: actively
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Actively
<hw>Ac"tive*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>In an active
manner; nimbly; briskly; energetically; also, by one's own action;
voluntarily, not passively.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Gram.)</fld> <def>In an active signification;
<as>as, a word used <ex>actively</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Activeness</ent>⟦br⟧
